title: Declaring and diagnosing research designs
text: declare_*() functions returns function. declare_model() (describes dimensions distributions variables, including potential outcomes) declare_inquiry() (takes variables model calculates estimand value) declare_sampling() (takes population selects sample) declare_assignment() (takes population sample adds treatment assignments) declare_measurement() (takes data adds measured values) declare_estimator() (takes data produced sampling, assignment, measurement returns estimates linked inquiries) declare_test() (takes data produced sampling, assignment, measurement returns result test) declare design, connect components design + operator. declared design, four core post-design-declaration commands used modify diagnose design: diagnose_design() (takes design returns simulations diagnosis) draw_data() (takes design returns single draw data) draw_estimates() (takes design returns single simulation estimates) draw_estimands() (takes design returns single simulation estimands) features: designer function takes parameters (e.g., N) returns design. expand_design() function designer parameters return design. can change diagnosands declare_diagnosands(). project generously supported grant Laura John Arnold Foundation seed funding EGAP.
